console.name: stdout
console.text:
1. Central circular arena structure (Madison Square Garden) defined by vertical beige beige ribs rendered as a repeating, tiled pixel texture.
2. Large, weathered circular roof featuring heavy cross-hatch dithering to mimic dirty concrete, with concentric rings of small, aliased vent sprites.
3. Tall adjacent rectangular skyscraper (Two Penn Plaza) featuring a rigid, high-contrast white grid facade with dark windows, strictly adhering to a repetitive pixel pattern.
4. Classical architecture building (Farley Post Office) in the upper left, rendered with distinct pixelated stone columns, jagged staircases, and flat limestone colors.
5. Rooftop parking deck on the lower-mid-rise building featuring rows of individual, non-blurry car sprites arranged in a grid.
6. Complex rooftop mechanical equipment, including HVAC units, fans, and water towers on the high-rise and surrounding buildings, rendered as sharp, isometric geometric shapes.
7. Asphalt street surfaces textured with noisy Bayer pattern dithering, featuring jagged, aliased white crosswalk lines and lane markers.
8. Surrounding low-rise mixed-use buildings in the bottom left corner using flat brick red and tan colors with tiled window grids.
9. A strictly limited, desaturated urban color palette (concrete greys, limestone tans, faded bricks) with no smooth gradients between shades.
10. Hard-edged, solid-color cast shadows (no transparency) projecting from the tower and arena onto the ground and adjacent structures.
